Docker Commands
Command	Description
docker-compose up	Start all services
docker-compose up --build	Rebuild and start all services
docker-compose down	Stop all services
docker-compose logs	View service logs
docker ps	List running containers
File Structure
text
eaud-cbdc/
├── docker-compose.yml     # Docker orchestration
├── eaud-api/
│   └── Dockerfile         # API container definition
└── eaud-ui/
    └── Dockerfile         # UI container definition
Troubleshooting
Issue	Solution
Port already in use	Stop existing services on ports 3000, 3001, 8080
Docker not running	Start Docker Desktop from Windows Start Menu
Keycloak connection refused	Wait 30 seconds for Keycloak to fully start
API cannot connect to Fabric	Ensure ./network.sh up is running in another terminal
